data.text: If I were to support any famous individuals for president it more likely be someone like Elon Musk, or someone tough with a scientific depth of understanding. Even if they weren't perfect on enemy, military issue, it's science will make security and mankinds future.

At first thought, I would not imagine voting for pres any of the individuals mentions in this article, believing they are too extremist liberal, mushy mushy, can’t we all get along. Russia, Iran, China, open door immigration, crime, other enemies would eat us alive.
